===[[Pokémon Mezastar]]===
Diantha, based on her appearance in {{aniseries|PTS}}, appeared in [[Pokémon Mezastar]]. In this game, Diantha is seen using {{p|Hawlucha}}, {{p|Gardevoir}}, {{p|Gourgeist}}, and {{p|Goodra}}. In the [[Double Chain set 1 (Mezastar)|first set in the Double Chain series]], Diantha also appeared as an opponent in an event that recreated the [[Masters Eight Tournament]] that ran from October 27 to November 21, 2022. Upon beating the character, the player can receive a Support Pokémon Ticket based on [[Diantha's Gardevoir]], which can [[Mega Evolution|Mega Evolve]].<ref>https://pokemonmezastar.com/event/e2210142/</ref>

